<figureCitation box="[374,442,1497,1523]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="9.[151,244,1935,1956]" captionTargetBox="[202,1384,229,1879]" captionTargetId="figure-41@9.[200,1386,197,1910]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bayesian posterior probability tree, with support indicated above branches: Bayesian posterior probabilities right of slash, maximum parsimony’s symmetric resampling values left of slash." pageId="17" pageNumber="50">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
